# Baseline Documentation Flow

- Keep docs consistent with current runtime behavior.
- Remove obsolete guidance rather than leaving conflicting alternatives.
- Add new docs to `docs/INDEX.md` with one-line purpose statements.
- Keep `docs/ONTOLOGY.md` and `data/ontology/schema.json` aligned when ontology behavior changes.
- Archive superseded plans in `docs/archive/`.
